snippet.title: Kaizo Mario World 3 - Stage 1
snippet.description:
Yes, you read that correctly. 

There is now a official third entry in the Kaizo Mario series. Crafted by the same person that created the first two, Kaizo Mario is back, full fucking force. 

If anyone is insane enough to play this, the link to IPS is here: https://skydrive.live.com/?cid=032864261776C9F9#cid=032864261776C9F9&id=32864261776C9F9!105
